name: Within the Clouds
description: This was taken in Arosa, Switzerland on the peak on the Weisshorn. It's 2,653m above sea level and while it's not the highest I've been. It's freaking high. On a clear day you can see as far as Chur and to the south across the Graubünden Alps to Piz Bernina. On this day however, I was within the clouds.
